<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b 0%, #38f9d7 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Welcome to SMS! 🎉</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;">
    <h2 style="color: #43e97b; margin-top: 0;">Hello {{name}}!</h2>
    
    <p>Welcome to the School Management System! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
    
    <p>Your account (<strong>{{email}}</strong>) has been successfully created. You can now access all the features of our platform:</p>
    
    <ul style="line-height: 2;">
      <li>📊 Real-time student performance tracking</li>
      <li>📅 Attendance management</li>
      <li>📝 Assignment and grade management</li>
      <li>🤖 AI-powered insights and analytics</li>
      <li>📈 Comprehensive reporting</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b 0%, #38f9d7 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">Login to Your Account</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      <strong>Need help getting started?</strong> Check out our documentation or contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>&copy; 2025 School Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>







